---
title: Trance Music
permalink: /trance-music/index.html
description: Weekly trance mixes featuring the best trance tracks
layout: page
sizes: '(max-width: 615px) 50vw, 100vw'
widths: [400, 520]
---

<article class="full section" style="--spot-color: var(--color-bg-accent)">
  {% svg "divider/soft-top", null, "seperator" %}

  <section class="feature section__inner wrapper">
    <p>
      Welcome to my trance music collection. Here you can find my weekly mixes featuring
      the best trance tracks. Most of my work is available on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@svenmalvik" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>. Every week, I curate
      and mix energetic trance sets that blend classic anthems with the latest releases from
      top trance producers.
    </p>

    <h2>Latest Productions & Mixes:</h2>
    <div
      class="feature grid region"
      style="--region-space-top: var(--space-s); --gutter: var(--space-m) var(--space-xs)"
    >
      <!-- Loop through trance music entries -->
      {% for track in tranceTracks %}
        <custom-card clickable img-square class="text-step-min-1" style="--card-bg: var(--color-bg); position: relative;">
          {% if track.youtube %}
            <div slot="image" style="margin-bottom: -1rem;">
              <div class="track-number">{{ track.episode }}</div>
              <img 
                src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/{{ track.youtube }}/mqdefault.jpg" 
                alt="Thumbnail for {{ track.title }}"
                style="width: 100%; max-height: 145px; object-fit: cover; display: block;"
              >
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          <h3 class="text-step-0" slot="headline">{{ track.title | safe }}</h3>

          <p slot="content">{{ track.description }}</p>
          <footer slot="footer" class="repel">
            <a class="no-indicator" href="{{ track.link }}">Listen on YouTube</a>
            <span class="gradient-text-linear">{{ track.duration }}</span>
          </footer>
        </custom-card>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {% svg "divider/soft-bottom", null, "seperator" %}
</article>

{% css "inline" %}
  {% include "css/custom-card.css" %}

  .track-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.5rem;
    left: 0.5rem;
    width: 3.5rem;
    height: 3.5rem;
    background: #BED629;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #343434;
    border: 4px solid var(--color-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    z-index: 10;
  }

  [slot="image"] {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }

  custom-card {
    overflow: visible !important;
  }
{% endcss %} 